Interface Distribution

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DistributionWithRandom
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BetaDistribution, ChiDistribution, ChiSquaredDistribution, ConstantDistribution, GammaDistribution, NormalDistribution, PoissonDistribution, StudentsTDistribution, UniformDistribution

    public interface Distribution
    Statistical distributions, with their common functions. See DistributionWithRandom for distributions that also have a random generator included.
